&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Killing the Menhir</span><hr size=1> Hehe, not surprising that lures didn't get through since they are currently broken.  Would be interesting to try again when, or rather if, they fix lures. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufaylaen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faylaen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/00 10:20:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/FB2001?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Killing the Menhir</span><hr size=1> Actually we engaged as well.  Hits for 115, so not that bad but seems to have HP out the Wazoo.  We couldn't land a spell either, course I am only lvl 53.<br><br>Heres an idea though. . . I was not in melee range.  Maybe you have to be.  No idea.<br><br>Faylaen<br>53 Wiz<br>Drinal <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ushardelay.showPublicProfile?language=EN>shardelay</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/16/00 3:21:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mehnir</span><hr size=1> was thinking maybe you ahve to give him something to stop him from exploding.  maybe our phenocryst focus eh just gave us.  of course i didnt have the balls to do this and just kept it.  Just a thought.<br><br>shard elay<br>56 wiz bertoz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uardoon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ardoon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/16/00 7:39:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Do not give the focus</span><hr size=1> An enchanter friend said the same thing, so when she tried it in Rodcet Nife she ended up giving him the Phenocryst Focus.  She lost the focus and nothing happened.  I guess someone had to try it.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usertaintkell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sertain TKell</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC= http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif .gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/18/00 12:31:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Killed Him</span><hr size=1> Well, after getting my crystal, a few of us were still around bsing when we saw this guy spawn.  And being the bored type, we decided to attack it.  After what seemed like years, we finally put the guy to rest, and ya he seemed to have nasty MR and lots of hps.  My lure spells did hit, just not all the time.  MAX dmg from his hits looks to be about 199. <br><br>And you ask.. Well, what did he drop?????<br><br>LOL what is it those kids say....Ph@t L2wtz! heh<br>Pearl Ring and a jasper!  <br>HAHAH  I about died laughing. <br><br><br>This is how we killed him.<br><br>3 necros, wiz, shaman, cleric and a druid.<br>The necros chain casted the pets and the druid would dmg shield them.  Cleric would heal necros as they were in lich form and would try to toss a timely CH to a pet if possible.  The druid would as pop the pets with life if possible.  I would run up and drop all my mana on him then go sit back on my arse and watch them do the rest.  Just a note, the cleric ended this with no mana, and 2 of the necros were about out too.  So, if you plan on killing him again to see if there is some rare drop, then grab another cleric and you should be fine.<br><br>Sertain T'Kell <br>Bristlebane <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=firionesterandir>FirionEsterandir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/15/01 8:57:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Test</span><hr size=1> Excuse me i just had to test if my account worked, sorry for any inconvenience <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showPrevMessage?topicID=3.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=3.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcomp